ÍĬǏÎÏḮİỊȈÌȊĪĮƗĨḬıllılı
İsmet Ιs not Ismet!
İbrahim Yıldız
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Göbekli Tepe

"Rosny aîné and the 1927"
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neanderthal

Symbols
